ên nguyên vận kỳ 1 - 和工部武灝澤詠蓮元韻其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0m-D%E1%BB%A5ng-Chi/K%C3%BD-H%E1%BB%A9a-h%E1%BA%A1-ti%E1%BB%81n-qu%E1%BA%A3n-k%C3%BD-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1/poem-Y4mzmGLAPtwdVedkUWBKXA">Ký Hứa hạ tiền quản ký Vương thị ngự - 寄許下前管記王侍禦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0m-D%E1%BB%A5ng-Chi/author-k_4EEx6yQhcGl5XMaCdIaA">Đàm Dụng Chi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/T%C3%A2n-M%C3%B9i-l%E1%BA%A1p-k%C3%BD-ch%C6%B0-%E1%BA%A5u-t%E1%BB%AD-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-t%C3%B4n-xu%C3%A2n-sam-th%C6%B0-gi%E1%BB%9Bi/poem-JkWTTek1-IkODY-WZaRORw">Tân Mùi lạp ký chư ấu tử đồng tôn xuân sam thư giới - 辛未臘寄諸幼子童孫春衫書戒</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-lfkyiRMg6zwt6_eiwas6Yg">Vũ Phạm Khải</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/Thi%E1%BB%87n-v%E1%BB%8B-chi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-7_zF-x1x1pienpNIOQCVKQ">Thiện vị chiếu - 禪位詔</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/author-kBTBt5Mbi6PPrH2sJkQAPw">Khuyết danh Việt Nam</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/Thu%E1%BA%ADt-ho%C3%A0i/poem-VV71m9js1bbdtwwLV_OtEQ">Thuật hoài - 述懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/author-DYGad0thHvgCxK3Szp1zVQ">Trần Đình Túc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-Mai-Pha/Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-mai-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-zSPC6PVp1fcZemvavfPMhQ">Tuyết mai kỳ 1 - 雪梅其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-Mai-Pha/author-RsrtOLmUMIuICsXh29zWQw">Lư Mai Pha</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
